org.ow2.proactive.resourcemanager.nodesource.common

Annotation Type Configurable


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value=FIELD)
public @interface Configurable
    Annotation for automatic GUI construction. This is a marker for GUI builder to include an annotated field into the GUI. Initial value of the field will be used in GUI as a string.
